dateText:
OCTOBER
20 Friday
Tum water - Wash Ter
fullText:
Mrs Martha Tower
Very small audience
Invited to amend Judge
DiGelouis bill on suffrage
lost by 16 to 11 - not
considered a test vote
summaryText: Susan B. Anthony attended a small audience in Tum water - Wash Ter and Mrs Martha Tower lost by 16 to 11 in an attempt to amend Judge DiGelouis bill on suffrage.
